Tools for creating opencpn packages.
====================================

These tools uses the packaging at https://github.com/opencpn/opencpn to
create debian packages and eventually a complete repository

- Copy the complete repo/ structure someplace else.
- Use podman and build.sh to create arm64 and amd64 packages, 
  move them to pool/
- Run tools/build-repo
- Done. Tar the directory, transfer and publish.

